{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a096d9e854","title":"象山县一反革命分子进行爆炸破坏","origin":"美国图书馆收藏","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ee64a7e88e","index":0,"year":1960,"month":1,"day":24,"articleId":"a096d9e854"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d8c5b6c7fa","type":"title","text":"象山县一反革命分子进行爆炸破坏","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a096d9e854"},{"id":"87c2ca5164","type":"paragraph","text":"1月24日，浙江象山县第一中学化验室突然爆炸，全部化学仪器和教学用具被烧毁，损失三千余元。经查实，这次爆炸是反革命分子、物理教员曹文开进行的反革命破坏。","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a096d9e854"},{"id":"ade6c92cd8","type":"paragraph","text":"曹出身于小土地出租者家庭，父亲和哥哥都是天主教神职人员，曹在1958年反右派斗争中受到小组批判，对我极端仇恨。曹在混进象山第一中学后，做了一支木质假手枪，油印了大量反动标语，进行反革命活动。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a096d9e854"},{"id":"7d6446769c","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：1960年2月18日新华通讯社编《内部参考》。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a096d9e854"}],"page":{"id":"8bc8a8701d","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a096d9e854","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}